snippet.title: The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt - Launch Cinematic
snippet.description:
"A Night to Remember", The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt launch cinematic, has arrived!

Feast your eyes on a gripping portrayal what The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt is all about and step into the shoes of professional monster hunter Geralt of Rivia in this gorgeous launch cinematic.

For more information about The Witcher visit:
Buy now: http://buy.thewitcher.com
Facebook: https://www.fb.com/thewitcher
Twitter: https://twitter.com/witchergame
Homepage: http://thewitcher.com/witcher3
Instagram: https://instagram.com/cdpred/
